}}
The Garbage lid is a low-value metal [[Scrap]] item. It is one of the only two-handed Scrap items in the game that is completely weightless, along with [[Hive]]s. Since it's made entirely out of metal, it will attract lightning during [[Stormy]] weather.

Despite how the player holds this item, the Garbage lid does '''not''' act as a shield and will not protect against any forms of damage.

== Trivia ==

<q>I've also noticed the garbage lid could look like a landmine.</q>&mdash;Zeekerss{{cite Patreon|date=2024-08-18|slug=gigantic-version-110315042|title=The Gigantic Version 60 Post}}
<br>As noted there, [[landmine]]s can easily be mistaken for Garbage lids (and vice-versa), which employees should be wary of when visiting a moon where the Garbage lid spawns.

The Garbage lid has a unique drop sound.

