Red soda.wikitext:
{{topicon Fandom}}
{{interlangbox}}
{{#invoke:Scraps/AutoInfobox|infobox
| scrap = SodaCanRed
}}
The '''Red soda''' is a low-to-high-value [[Scrap]] with a design resembling a Coca-Cola can, except the text simply reads “SODA”. The tab of the can has been opened, so it's implied to be an empty tin can despite weighing multiple pounds. The bottom of the can reads "2 FL OZ.", despite being in the shape of a traditional 12 fl oz soda can.

As it is made of metal, a Red Soda can trigger lightning strikes when held by an employee or when on the ground during [[stormy]] weather.

== Trivia ==

It's possible the text at the bottom was originally supposed to say "12 FL OZ." but the 1 was erased because it was funny. This could also double as an explanation for why the Red soda is so heavy in-game, as most of the space inside the can may be occupied by metal to leave only enough space for 2 fl oz. of fluid.

